                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I can get up to 80% failures on pacification at hard. 
<br />

<br />
Just don't bother and mez. And your party might want to maximize these defensive skills before doing them.
<br />

<br />
As far as strats goes - well it's basic dungeon crawling except it's pretty hardcore. One thing that might help is to have a target ready to be mezzed before pulling. In some dungeons like Guk and miragul you'll want malo to help with charm or you might just be wasting your time recharming your pet over and over.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
