                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">its been my experience that even with time geared group you are most likey going to need charm to win, and definately need charm to win in under an hour.
<br />

<br />
if you arent good at charming / dont have enouugh hps to live thru a break, keep doing easy missions til u have enough gear to do so. Dont bother with LR5 it does nothing except make you feel warm and fuzzy. It certainly shouldnt be something you depend on. You should have at least 4k hps buffed to do hard. And its pretty easy to get 5k hps buffed without any raid loot from elementals. With 5k hps + arcane rune you can live thru a charm break np. Most healer have a hot key to help out enchanters whos pets are bashing their brains in, that helps too.
<br />

<br />
Dont quad your pet til you have 6k+ hps and dont haste+quad til u have 7k+ Thats my rule of thumb.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><img src="http://strike9.com/file.ashx?path=%2fVizier%2ffullsize%2fVizierSig4.jpg" border="0" />
