                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As we find normal adventures too easy, my usual group has 
<br />
graduated to hard missions.
<br />

<br />
We did 4 hard adventures this weekend and won them all, none of
<br />
us is even remotely well geared ( no VT gear, no Elementals ).
<br />
So yes it can be done, just takes some skill  and teamwork. My 
<br />
record is now won 7 lost 2 on hard. The 2 losses were due to
<br />
crappy zones, 1 where there was 5-7 mobs in rooms and a 
<br />
rescue mission in a large linear dunegon which we ran out of 
<br />
time when we had killed 60 mobs and we we needed another 40
<br />
or so to get to hostage. These are really challenging for us, we 
<br />
can have 2-4 deaths per mission.
<br />

<br />
I don't use pacify as its resisted too much. We pre-target mobs 
<br />
where possible. Have won once using a charmed pet. Finding the
<br />
particular mob that can be charmed and a blue con is pure luck.
<br />
Augments and named mobs seem very rare. Chest loots are just
<br />
as crap as in normal  ( though we did once get a +7 augment in 
<br />
one)
<br />

<br />

