                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Samiel wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">If you have some threads indicating CHA helps with Mezz can you link some for me? </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Samiel, look here: <a href="http://forums.crgaming.com/eqbb/viewtopic.php?t=22981" target="_blank">http://forums.crgaming.com/eqbb/viewtopic.php?t=22981</a>
