<br />
That's an OLD test, so the results may no longer be valid.  However, I *believe* that they are still true in general, though the numbers might have changd a little.
<br />

<br />
In summary, YES charisma effects Mez.  However, the effect is fairly small, so focusing your efforts on Hp/AC/AA may give more benefit to you.  Which is what the debate has really been -- yes, cha has an effect, but is it enough of one to bother with?
