                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Im usually the puller for hard adventures when we do em. The trick imo is what mob to mezz in a room of 4+ so you only get 1-2 coming to camp. 
<br />

<br />
Im top on my server in high risk wins with 85 atm and i have only done 1 in the last 2-3 weeks. I charm every chance i get, but just to be a tad more safe, i only haste it when i have 2 healers in the group and a bard to mezz it when it breaks. 
<br />

<br />
Yes usually i could get it back either way, but im not happy with "usually" i want to survive every damn time so i use a tad more precaution than tojust haste every damn one (well unless its one of those stupid caster holgresh)
<br />

<br />
Pacification is a total waste of time on high risk imo, the mana cost is huge for something that doesnt work 80% of the time, id rather just mezz and have 2-3 come to camp(if mezz is resisted i get 3 at times) 
<br />

<br />
I pull with boggle when i can. Im one of the few i guess that believes boggle works, not as well as it should, but it still works. I almost never keep aggro on the mobs i pulled once the tank hits them one time. Id love to use dispell to pull but i just dont have the spell slots for that.
<br />

<br />
If i pull more than i should..i just send in the pet to tank them all untill the adds are mezzed then the tank  just assists pet and we are gtg. 
<br />

<br />
I have one rule for all my group members in high risk...dont move up untill i say so. I had a shaman once run up on a big pull of 5 that my pet was running up to tank, shaman casted slow..got aggro...got scared and ran back to the group. Which meant that the cleric had to heal the MT soon..which meant he couldnt heal my pet when it  got near death..and bam we got too many on us and we wiped. 
<br />

<br />
If you are a puller..make sure your group knows how to work with you before you start..or crap like this can and will happen.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Sage Trazer Adept
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22957" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=22957</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
